snippet.title: NEGATIVE REVERIE - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Negative Reverie is a modern-day RPG set in a Silicon Valley-style Tech City run by the FamilyTech Company. You play as Vuota, a woman with a hacksaw and a mission to assassinate the FamilyTech CEO. Along the way, she and her allies stumble upon a dark secret underpinning their society and possibly humanity at large....

Wishlist now on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3328380/Negative_Reverie

Music & Soundeffects by DonutShoes:
https://donutshoes.bandcamp.com/

Character Design, Cutscenes, Art by Maizilla:
https://maizilla.com/

Story & Programming by TwirlinCurtis:
https://bsky.app/profile/twirlincurtis.bsky.social
